# manifest.json is the live list of all active Cloudflare zones, generated by
# scripts/sync-cf-zones-to-manifest.sh from the Cloudflare API (via CI/MCP —
# never a token in chat). It is regenerated per deploy and must NOT be committed:
# a stale committed manifest would be cross-checked by verify-domains.yml and
# could ship outdated zone_ids or cause confusing failures.
manifest.json
